HEADWORD: Herapathite
<hw>Her"a*path*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Named after
Dr. <ets>Herapath</ets>, the discoverer.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
